马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 招募戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl)、Slash 等人来推动继父的乐队foreigner 入围 2024 年摇滚名人堂：“让他们进来！” https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-ronson-recruits-dave-grohl-slash-and-more-to-boost-stepdads-band-foreigners-2024-rock-roll-hall-of-名气-出价-让-em-in-3591268？utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mark-ronson-recruits-dave-grohl-slash-and-more-to-boost-stepdads-band-foreigners-2024-rock-roll-名人堂竞标让他们进入Liberty DunworthThu, 22 Feb 2024 10:12:28 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3591268 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Slash、马克·朗森、米克·琼斯和戴夫·格罗尔" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该乐队自 2002 年起就有资格获得资格，但刚刚获得首次提名</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-ronson-recruits-dave-grohl-slash-and-more-to-boost-stepdads-band-foreigners-2024-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-bid-let-em-in-3591268">马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 招募戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl)、Slash 等人来推动继父的乐队foreigner 入围 2024 年摇滚名人堂：“让他们进来！”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Slash、马克·朗森、米克·琼斯和戴夫·格罗尔" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mark-Ronson-Foreigner@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-ronson">马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson)</a>招募了一些摇滚界的巨星来帮助推动<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foreigner">外国人</a>进入 2024 年摇滚名人堂。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/barbie-soundtrack-mark-ronson-interview-3473687">马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 如何成为好莱坞配乐之王：“‘芭比娃娃’感觉很特别”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位制作人因与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)</a>合作以及为<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/barbie-soundtrack-review-film-3471113"><em>芭比娃娃</em>配乐</a>而闻名，与乐队有着密切的联系，吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-jones">米克·琼斯 (Mick Jones)</a>是他的继父。</p><p>尽管自 2002 年以来就有资格获得摇滚名人堂提名，但今年早些时候，这些摇滚乐队首次获得了摇滚名人堂提名。</p><p>现在，在今年的提名公布后，他推动乐队进入克利夫兰音乐厅，并招募了一些大牌来帮助建立支持。</p><p> “让我想成为一名唱片制作人的一切都来自于在录音室里观看外国人制作唱片，”他在 Instagram 的最新更新中写道。</p><p> “我仍然对前五张专辑的声音感到非常敬畏。吉他神气十足，咬牙切齿。沉重的鼓，像穆塔一样与低音一起律动。广泛的合成器层。然后就是那个声音。还有那些歌曲。这真的很疯狂，”他补充道。 “这也有点疯狂，这是他们在 20 年后第一次参加摇滚名人堂的投票。”</p><p>在分享的视频中，罗森展示了他聚集起来支持他的摇滚皇室成员——包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">喷火战机</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">红辣椒</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">枪炮玫瑰</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">石器时代女王</a>的成员。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C3lJxeQvPUX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;u