rder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>麦克雷凭借第二张专辑 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tate-mcrae-think-later-review-lyrics-tracklist-3555092">《Think Later》</a> （2023 年）中的主打单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tate-mcrae-perform-greedy-and-grave-on-saturday-night-live-3543455">《Greedy》</a>获得全英音乐奖年度国际歌曲类别提名。她的对手包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-barbie-what-was-i-made-for-3468293">《我是为了什么？》</a> ）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sza-channel-her-inner-uma-thurman-in-bloody-new-video-for-kill-bill-3378444">《杀死比尔》</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodirgo-shares-rock-opera-inspired-new-track-vampire-3463529">《吸血鬼》</a> ）。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-here-are-all-the-nominees-3576382">您可以在此处查看 2024 年全英音乐奖提名者的完整名单</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tate-mcrae-think-later-review-lyrics-tracklist-3555092">《Think Later》的四星评论</a>中写道：“麦克雷显然仍在与自己的野心作斗争。然而，《Think Later》包含了足够的阴谋，表明这是一位艺术家最终磨练自己身份、一路跳舞、闪闪发光的作品。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-announces-final-headliner-3591184">2024 年全英音乐奖宣布最终头条新闻后</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
